Author: Marie-Pierre Sylvestre <marie-pierre.sylvestre@umontreal.ca>, Marie-Eve Beauchamp <marie-eve.beauchamp@clinepi.mcgill.ca>, Ryan Patrick Kyle <ryan.kyle@mail.mcgill.ca>, Michal Abrahamowicz <michal.abrahamowicz@mcgill.ca>
